ition</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(char : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic#L787-L792","name":"Unicode.getCanonicalCombiningClass","line":787,"kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getCanonicalCombiningClass","doc":"Get canonical combining class of character\n\nUnicode property: `Canonical_Combining_Class`\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getCanonicalCombiningClass\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">getCanonicalCombiningClass</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(char : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic#L769-L777","name":"Unicode.getTitleChar","line":769,"kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getTitleChar","doc":"Map character to titlecase\n\nThis function does not handle the case where the titlecase mapping would\nconsist of more than one character.\n\nUnicode property: `Simple_Titlecase_Mapping` "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getTitleChar\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">getTitleChar</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(char : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a></div></div>"},{