ata for `isCaseIgnorable`\n\nExtracted from UCD `auxiliary/WordBreakProperty.txt`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isCaseIgnorable.other\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">isCaseIgnorable</span>.<span class=\"name\">other</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt32\">UInt32</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic#L700-L725","name":"Unicode.isCaseIgnorable","line":700,"kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isCaseIgnorable","doc":"Check if character is ignorable for casing purposes\n\nGenerated from general categories `Lm`, `Mn`, `Me`, `Sk`, `Cf`, and word\nbreak properties `MidLetter`, `MidNumLet`, `Single_Quote`.\n\nUnicode property: `Case_Ignorable` "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isCaseIgnorable\"><span class=\"name\">Unicode</span>.<span class=\"name\">isCaseIgnorable</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(char : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic#L686-L691","name":"Unicode.isCased","line":686,"kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isCased","doc":"Check if cased letter character\n\nGenerated by `General_Category=LC | Other_Lowercase | Other_Uppercase`.\n\nUnicode property: `Cased` "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./UnicodeBa